snippet: The New York Knicks reclaimed their distinction as the NBA's most valuable team, worth $3 billion, according to a Forbes poll released on Wednesday that showed the average team value rose 13 percent from last year....
lead_paragraph: The New York Knicks reclaimed their distinction as the NBA's most valuable team, worth $3 billion, according to a Forbes poll released on Wednesday that showed the average team value rose 13 percent from last year.

headline.main: Knicks Reclaim Top Spot as Forbes' Most Valuable NBA Team
headline.print_headline: Knicks Reclaim Top Spot as Forbes' Most Valuable NBA Team
